MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- services/imagegen.py: Pillow-based brand card + matplotlib candle charts + tier progress card
- services/keyboards.py: persistent ReplyKeyboard main menu + inline CTAs (open PO, ref share, win/loss)
- handlers/start.py: send brand card photo with welcome caption + activate persistent keyboard; deep-link supports ref_<code> and po_<click_id>
- handlers/signals.py: render candle chart per signal with direction overlay; inline win/loss feedback buttons
- handlers/menu.py: routes for keyboard buttons + /calc + /leaderboard + /notifications
- formatter.py: format_signal_caption (compact, ▰▱ confidence bar)
- db: click_id, deposit_total, notifications_enabled, wins, losses columns + helpers
- main.py: register menu router last (catches keyboard text)
- requirements: Pillow, matplotlib, numpy, httpx
